list.name: Photography Cyborg
list.about: The Photography Cyborg is a character from the animated series Rick and Morty. He is a robotic being that specializes in capturing photographs. A curious fact about the Photography Cyborg is that his design and concept are a parody of the Cybermen from the long-running British science fiction series, Doctor Who. The Photography Cyborg's metallic appearance and robotic enhancements pay homage to the iconic villains known as the Cybermen. This clever crossover reference adds an extra layer of enjoyment for fans who appreciate the blending of different science fiction universes within the show.

list.name: Photography Raptor
list.about: The Photography Raptor is a character from the animated series Rick and Morty. A curious fact about the Photography Raptor is that its design and concept are a playful nod to the character Blue from the Jurassic Park franchise. The Photography Raptor's appearance and occupation as a photographer mirror Blue's role as one of the trained velociraptors in the Jurassic Park series. This amusing reference showcases the show's ability to incorporate elements from popular culture and create humorous connections between different fictional universes.
